                     <interp inst="t18080406-63-off336" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080406-63-cd337" type="crimeDate">5th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080406-63-off336 t18080406-63-cd337"></join>, two sheets; value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080406-63-victim604" type="victimName">
