               <p>Second count for like offence, and a shirt, value 2 s. the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080406-63-victim606" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Bligh
                  <interp inst="t18080406-63-victim606" type="surname" value="Bligh"></interp>
